<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to Biryani Junction!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
        }
        .welcome-message {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #e65100;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .features {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Biryani Junction!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="welcome-message">
            <h2>Dear {{name}},</h2>
            <p>Thank you for joining Biryani Junction! We're excited to have you as part of our family.</p>
            <p>Get ready to experience the most authentic and delicious biryanis delivered right to your doorstep.</p>
            
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{menuUrl}}" class="cta-button">Explore Our Menu</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="features">
            <h3>What you can do with your account:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Order your favorite biryanis online</li>
                <li>Track your orders in real-time</li>
                <li>Save your favorite items</li>
                <li>Get exclusive offers and discounts</li>
                <li>Manage your delivery addresses</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="special-offer">
            <h3>Special Welcome Offer!</h3>
            <p>Use code <strong>WELCOME10</strong> to get 10% off on your first order!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Follow us on social media for updates and special offers:</p>
            <p>
                <a href="{{socialLinks.facebook}}" style="margin: 0 10px;">Facebook</a>
                <a href="{{socialLinks.instagram}}" style="margin: 0 10px;">Instagram</a>
                <a href="{{socialLinks.twitter}}" style="margin: 0 10px;">Twitter</a>
            </p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at support@biryanijunction.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
